  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Professional development  Research Management and Governance (Phase 1)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting professional development of researchers, research managers and policymakers in areas of importance to science, technology and innovation. The programme builds capacity incountry to better allow researchers to pursue research that benefits their economy and solve development challenges.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The programme aims to review current research management and governance framework and identify needs for improvement, to evaluate and adapt some of the UK  best practices in research management and governance  and to make recommendations for improvement of research management and governance in Malaysia</narrative>
  </description>
